Git Commands

Clone/Download project
=> git clone https://github.com/shinderahul/tuts.git

To check repo status
=> git status

To Tracked/Add a single file
=> git add README.md

OR

To Tracked/Add all files
=> git add .

To unstage file to untrack
=> git rm --cached README.md

To commit file
=> git commit -m "Added style to header"

To push code
=> git push

To clear Terminal
=> cls

To check branch name
=> git branch

To restore back our changes
=> git restore style.css

